{"id": "1431815705157832704", "channel_id": "1431695221720350850", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "谢谢你！", "timestamp": "2025-10-26T01:24:25.959000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1176457149254209597"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431751908317593741", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431695221720350850", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：V2.4 忘却篇主线调整 Preview: V2.4 Faded Legacy Main Story Adjustments", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1431817233361010688", "channel_id": "1431695221720350850", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "很抱歉，为了在有限的预算和团队规模保证质量和成员的长期身心健康，甚至为未来的3.0投入前置规划，我们不得不放慢主线的更新速度。\n\nV1.0时代我们还有很多角色设定存货，所以可以更聚焦于主线，也是因为这样即便是团队最黑暗时期我们也跟变魔术一样拿出了V2.0。但我们现在越来越多的角色是全新制作，虽然一定程度上我们比V1.7时代扩大了团队，但这可能比大家想象的要更有挑战。", "timestamp": "2025-10-26T01:30:30.311000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["484622919943716864"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431796323387969567", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431695221720350850", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：V2.4 忘却篇主线调整 Preview: V2.4 Faded Legacy Main Story Adjustments", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1431817928537407609", "channel_id": "1431695221720350850", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "尤其是今年上半年，几乎只有很少的人，新招团队成员就算加入也要重新适应工作。而下半年本来就不多的美术成员经过一次重要重组，所以可以看到风格上我们都出现了一些波动。事实上我们差点因为美术团队的重建问题而再度断更。不过目前已经逐渐恢复正轨。", "timestamp": "2025-10-26T01:33:16.054000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431695221720350850", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：V2.4 忘却篇主线调整 Preview: V2.4 Faded Legacy Main Story Adjustments", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
