{"id": "1431874714933919814", "channel_id": "1431695221720350850", "type": 19, "author_id": "300996642532884490", "author_name": "mikamisono._.", "author_bot": false, "content": "Do you feel like it might be better to leave Normal mode chapters as is, and slightly reworking the difficulty for Hard Mode Faded Legacy?\n\nSome of the stages do feel like a slog to push through starting from ch6 onwards", "timestamp": "2025-10-26T05:18:54.986000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431695221720350850", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431695221720350850", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：V2.4 忘却篇主线调整 Preview: V2.4 Faded Legacy Main Story Adjustments", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1431886504166297621", "channel_id": "1431695221720350850", "type": 0, "author_id": "1220722226752651355", "author_name": "melody60925", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@633215996508766229> 可否詢問,關於中文官方臉書貼上的活動資訊,已經多次都只有英文活動資訊,沒有中文活動資訊,並不是每個臉書的人都有Discord的帳號,在臉書上有反映在這邊也有反應,但都並未得到答覆,中文臉書官方放置英文資訊活動是不是本末倒置??要放也是請以中文資訊先放再放英文吧?!不是嗎??麻煩請校貓答覆!!不然對只用臉書上看資訊的人很不公平", "timestamp": "2025-10-26T06:05:45.758000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431695221720350850", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：V2.4 忘却篇主线调整 Preview: V2.4 Faded Legacy Main Story Adjustments", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
