{"id": "1431901600435408926", "channel_id": "1431695221720350850", "type": 0, "author_id": "452516689225973761", "author_name": "thpdom", "author_bot": false, "content": "<:Cheerup:1400771555939844149>", "timestamp": "2025-10-26T07:05:44.989000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431695221720350850", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：V2.4 忘却篇主线调整 Preview: V2.4 Faded Legacy Main Story Adjustments", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1431913508274049055", "channel_id": "1431695221720350850", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "发布资讯的语言策略上的确有变化。为了聚焦制作精力、避免繁体中文的官方用语与当地审核冲突导致的时间耗损，新资讯以后我们只用英文和简中。同时据我所知因为一些多方合作原因我们目前不便在脸书上发布简中内容。于是脸书就有些尴尬。未来有空我们会整理这一点。如果要关注讯息还是请在游戏内或DC。", "timestamp": "2025-10-26T07:53:04.039000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1220722226752651355"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431886504166297621", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431695221720350850", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "前瞻：V2.4 忘却篇主线调整 Preview: V2.4 Faded Legacy Main Story Adjustments", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
